{"tid":476799,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"電視廣播有限公司董事方逸華離世 享年83歲","createTime":"2017-11-22T10:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T11:10:07.000Z","uid":38946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"90920905f878496359b2fefd8365658b02c28f4a","tid":476799,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"據無綫新聞報道指電視廣播有限公司董事方逸華因病安祥離世，享年83歲。據悉方逸華今日在養和醫院病逝，喪禮事宜將另行公佈。<br />\n<br />\n方逸華原名李夢蘭，邵逸夫的第二任妻子，她於1931年於上海出生，方逸華於1952年登台期間，認識丈夫邵逸夫，1969年入邵氏兄弟電影公司，1988年入無綫電視董事局，方逸華在2012年向無綫電視董事局辭任副主席兼董事總經理，過半退休生活，今年並沒出席無綫台慶活動。李寶安回覆《蘋果》稱&quot;Already on TVB News.&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171122/57490710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171122%2F57490710&d=zHqKsc4XsIYGQJODhmHhQ5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=20f19ef3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171122%2F57490710&h=c7f24c8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171122/57490710</a>"},{"pid":"a7d1fbfb14ff28accaef8a7be2c7d8947e9c3138","tid":476799,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7c6b31996c208238a715fc9055cb7a04c92b9b","tid":476799,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:10:07.000Z","msg":"我啱啱睇蘋果 以為六叔又死多次..."}]}